<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        main {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto; 
        }
        footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); 
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
<header>
  <nav class="h-24 border-gray-200 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 via-gray-800 to-gray-950">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between mx-auto p-7">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center space-x-3 rtl:space-x-reverse">
        <span class="self-center text-3xl font-semibold whitespace-nowrap text-white">Sportopia</span>
      </a>
      <button data-collapse-toggle="navbar-solid-bg" type="button" class="inline-flex items-center p-2 w-10 h-10 justify-center text-sm text-gray-300 rounded-lg md:hidden hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
        <span class="sr-only">Open main menu</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 17 14">
          <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 1h15M1 7h15M1 13h15" />
        </svg>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden w-full md:block md:w-auto" id="navbar-solid-bg">
        <ul class="flex flex-col font-medium mt-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 md:space-x-8 rtl:space-x-reverse md:flex-row md:mt-0 md:border-0 md:bg-transparent">
          <li>
            <a href="/" class="block py-2 px-3 text-2xl md:p-0 text-white bg-blue-700 rounded md:bg-transparent hover:text-blue-300 md:hover:text-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-800">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/about" class="block py-2 px-3 text-2xl md:p-0 text-gray-200 hover:text-blue-300">About</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#features" class="block py-2 px-3 text-2xl md:p-0 text-gray-200 hover:text-blue-300">Features</a>
          </li>
          <% if (user) { %>
            <li>
              <a href="/logout" class="block py-2 px-3 text-2xl md:p-0 text-gray-200 hover:text-blue-300">Logout</a>
            </li>
          <% } else { %>
            <li>
              <a href="/login" class="block py-2 px-3 text-2xl md:p-0 text-gray-200 hover:text-blue-300">Login/Register</a>
            </li>
          <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
  
</header>

<main>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-4">
    <p class="mt-2 text-3xl text-center pt-14">Elevate your sports experience...</p>
<p class="mt-2 text-3xl text-center pt-2">with Sportopia!</p>
<p class="mt-2 text-xl text-center pt-4">Connect with players, organize matches, and stay ahead in the game. Join now!</p>


<section id="features" class="mt-12 mb-24">
  <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">Key Features</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center card">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3M16 7V3M3 8h18M4 12h16m-1 8h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5H9v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5m10 0h2"></path>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Game Scheduling</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Plan and organize your games seamlessly with our advanced scheduling system.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-700 text-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center card">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 20h10m-5-16a2 2 0 110 4 2 2 0 010-4zM4 15a4 4 0 014-4h8a4 4 0 014 4v1H4v-1z"></path>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Team Management</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Easily create and manage teams, assign tasks, and evaluate performance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-700 text-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center card">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 17a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"></path>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Performance Analytics</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Get comprehensive insights into player stats and team performance metrics.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-yellow-700 text-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center card">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 11l7 7 7-7M3 5h18"></path>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Leaderboard Tracking</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Keep up with real-time rankings and leaderboards for all your games.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-700 text-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center card">
      <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h10M7 11h10m-5 4h5M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
      </svg>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Mobile Optimization</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Enjoy full functionality and seamless access on mobile devices.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



<section id="testimonials" class="mt-12 mb-24">
  <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">What Our Users Say</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    
