        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold ml-3 text-gray-900">John Carter</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">"Sportopia revolutionized how we organize sports events. The intuitive platform made scheduling and team coordination effortless."</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-100 to-green-50 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9V7a4 4 0 018 0v2m0 4v2m0 3h0a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4a2 2 0 01-2-2h0"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold ml-3 text-gray-900">Sophia Reynolds</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">"The analytics provided by Sportopia give us valuable insights into team performance, helping us improve game strategies."</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-purple-50 rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9V7a4 4 0 018 0v2m0 4v2m0 3h0a2 2 0 01-2 2h-4a2 2 0 01-2-2h0"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold ml-3 text-gray-900">David Mitchell</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">"The mobile-friendly interface ensures I can manage everything on the go. Sportopia is a game-changer for sports organizers."</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

  </div>
</main>

<footer class="bg-gray-800 py-6">
  <div class="w-full mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
    <!-- Branding and Text -->
    <span class="text-xl text-white font-semibold text-center md:text-left">
      © 2023 <a href="/" class="hover:underline text-blue-400">Sportopia™</a>. All Rights Reserved.
    </span>
    
    <!-- Navigation Links -->
    <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-end gap-6 mt-4 md:mt-0">
      <li>
        <a href="/about" class="text-white text-lg hover:text-blue-400 hover:underline">About</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-white text-lg hover:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/licensing" class="text-white text-lg hover:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Licensing</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-white text-lg hover:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Contact</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</footer>


</body>
</html>
